snippet.title: Sudoku Topology announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Explore classic sudoku variant rules on 3D boards ranging from cubes and spheres to dodecahedron and the Klein bottle. Experience beautiful logic of handcrafted puzzles where no guessing is required. Or design your own 3D sudoku puzzles and share them with the world!
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3051910/Sudoku_Topology/
